Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫做克劳德˙肯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能够揭发『魔石索沙』所隐藏的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便和蕾娜开始朝着艾尔大陆前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经…等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少用你们那双脏手随便碰我!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来在途中遇到了纹章术师塞丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又和一个叫做艾修顿的剑客变成了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我体内沉睡红莲之火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉火王派蒙之名解放你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请依圣三角的引导
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将站在我眼前的愚昧者，给予灼热的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳为什么要离开阿利亚村
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还跟那两个家伙一起旅行呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在找魔石索沙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和克劳德为了调查魔石索沙的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以必须到艾尔大陆去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我听说魔石索沙带来的危险 根本超乎我们的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳怎么还会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当这块大地－艾克斯贝尔受到欺凌民不聊生之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便会出现一位异国打扮的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者高举着光剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救苦难的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德就是传说中的这位勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:03:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好朋友…啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为了帮他们寻宝和驱魔，虽然多绕了一点远路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过折腾了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算到达了克洛斯大陆东部的港湾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是哈利啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里热热闹闹的，挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海风吹起来也好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要把谜底解开…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事啊我们待会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先找间旅馆好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了每天餐风露宿的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.26,Top,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不要拉我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子好饿、背酸得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发干燥，皮肤也快干死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾修顿呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说也对耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真会给人添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个没用的剑客到底跑到哪里去了嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(来看一看啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(新到的货色哪)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(我这里的货色最齐全哪)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请问你，到底要摸到什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你们的朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点把他弄走好不好啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这是克洛斯l3世纪的橡木桶欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种遥远又古老的香味…\N你一定装过白兰地对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真香，闻到我都快要醉倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚刚到现在就是这样没离开过耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他该不会是个…迷恋酒桶的收集狂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么收集狂啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上有这种人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卖你们5000弗尔就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很贵吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要买啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还真的要背着这个大酒桶去艾尔大陆啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要傻了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是艾修顿他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠们都在向你求救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样…就买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个酒桶该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,25午前在卡利亚工房限量生产的…桧木酒桶吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便他了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小长和小圆不会有什么事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经把塞丽奴的帽子挂在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他应该很快就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像他那种人啊…为他担心根本是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样倒也罢了，要是迷路的话怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜，妳就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛斯国王给我们的通行证\N能不能借给我看看呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…哪里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好象…看不到海了耶?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们…是迷路啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有，没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想休息的时候，我们去看要搭的船吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是，我们马上就要过海了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是得整顿一下心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎哟…有没有搞错啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的腿肿得这么厉害好惨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳又来了，那妳先等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就去拿一些热水来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太感激妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂~喂~喂~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪，眼睛突然有一点刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是灰尘跑进去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是睫毛长反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那妳最好不要揉得太用力，我来帮妳看一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴姐也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过，她的纹章术会帮上克劳德不少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不要计较这些事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴姐，热水…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜、蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~太好了…碰上好人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该也听到蕾娜说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才，从她站的位置看起来，也难怪她会误会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差那么多…不会吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们…竟然接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩个搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道一定是妳，蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪，我们能在这里碰面还真是巧耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…我们离山越来越近了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是方向…好象错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么啊你?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把房间钥匙通通都交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们兄弟要到你这里来找样宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请妳下次再来捧场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜，对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…蕾娜，妳会不会吃得太多啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土产吃太多肚子会胀耶?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓，我要全部吃光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃东西的时候不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，喝点水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳还好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德也太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是这件事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他自己说这趟旅行可能要豁出性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然…竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还做出那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要继续不停的吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.96,Top,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀蕾娜 好了啦!妳冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳放手，放手放手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么『整顿一下心情』嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.50,Top,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我才不要跟着他 妳就让我继续吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.68,Top,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦，不要闹了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是克劳德他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来不像是这样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲眼看到的不可能错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…妳要回阿利亚村喽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果妳不想跟他一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在这里也不是办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点，先溜为妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德在里面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛，明明是你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…那是我的包包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕，快溜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等，把我的包包还我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以，妳追去太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是通行证在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强盗、有强盗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.44,0:13:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不是小雪吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳怎么会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些待会再说!蕾娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想念妳啊…妳好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你的样子好象不怎么好哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了一件大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把包包还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人还不死心啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可见这里面的东西很重要欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它还给我、还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不还
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海水怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，通行证…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜，妳没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，快抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜，妳快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空…破…斩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德、克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通行证…被人偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不能怪妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事都要怪我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用跟我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.86,0:16:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为塞丽奴姐人那么好，长得又好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳错了
